headline: A Fresh Look at United Rentals (URI) Valuation After Wells Fargo’s New “Overweight” Coverage
summary: Wells Fargo has just initiated coverage on United Rentals (URI) with an “Overweight” rating, reinforcing recent positive sentiment from analysts. headline: Here’s the Good News and the Bad News. 4 Calls From a Top Economist.
summary: You won’t catch Tom Porcelli,  Wells Fargo’s  new chief economist, lamenting the lack of economic data on hand these days.  Although the record-breaking government shutdown has delayed critical federally produced measures of employment, inflation, and economic activity, Porcelli says economists and Federal Reserve officials are far from operating completely in the dark.  Porcelli, who most recently served as chief U.S. economist at PGIM Fixed Income, joined Wells Fargo as chief economist on Nov. 3.
